Package com.rubynaxela.kyanite.util.data

Class JSONDataFile

java.lang.Object
java.io.File
com.rubynaxela.kyanite.util.data.DataFile
com.rubynaxela.kyanite.util.data.JSONDataFile
All Implemented Interfaces:
Dictionary, Serializable, Comparable<File>, Map<String,Object>
public class JSONDataFile extends DataFile implements Dictionary
Representation of a physical JSON-formatted file at the specified path. Provides methods for reading and writing the values as values of specific Java types.
